# A wooden deck with wheels. Typically consists of a wooden plank (circa 7.75" wide and 32" long), two metal trucks (axles) each with two urethane wheels (circa 54mm in diameter). The top part of the deck has [[grip tape]] glued to it, which is similar to a sand-paper like material. Related articles: [[skateboard deck]], [[skateboard trucks]], [[skateboard wheels]], [[grip tape]], [[skateboarding]].